questions : how secure is apple pay?
identiy: 55% of people in the world have an iPhone and each iPhone has a specific IMEI number attached to it. This allows everyone to have an account tied to their phone in addation this allows each of those transactions to be tracked. Detouring fraud and other activities.
connections: all iPhone can have access to the internet. This allows them to connect to the cloud for purchase. Also within the phone you can connect using NFC.
combining the two: with all of these build in measures to track the cardholer. The cardholder needs protections and that is where they will be issues an EMV token with thier digital wallet
